Shim Soo-in?

290
00:29:45,225 --> 00:29:46,783
Do you know them?

291
00:29:48,161 --> 00:29:51,858
So that's who
you were looking for

292
00:29:52,899 --> 00:29:55,697
Sure, I know them
since they were famous

293
00:29:55,935 --> 00:29:58,665
They were very sick

294
00:29:59,873 --> 00:30:04,105
