and Kyung-hee passed away

302
00:30:44,350 --> 00:30:46,147
Pardon?

303
00:30:47,587 --> 00:30:52,456
What are you talking about?
Kyung-hee's dead?

304
00:30:53,927 --> 00:30:56,794
Yes, it's so awful

305
00:30:57,563 --> 00:31:01,363
