306
00:31:03,102 --> 00:31:06,230
It's been five years already

307
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:10,974
Kyung-hee's dead?
Kyung-hee?

308
00:31:15,682 --> 00:31:18,207
Soo-in will be hard to find

309
00:31:18,451 --> 00:31:20,620
After Kyung-hee died,

310
00:31:20,620 --> 00:31:23,817
