311
00:31:24,390 --> 00:31:25,687
She had it hard

312
00:31:25,792 --> 00:31:29,057
Since they relied on
each other so much

313
00:31:33,933 --> 00:31:37,994
Holding back my wish
to scribble with you together

314
00:31:38,738 --> 00:31:41,366
But Min-sik
will be in late today

315
00:31:41,674 --> 00:31:44,643
Can you tell me
where I find him?

316
00:32:44,837 --> 00:32:47,271
Ji-hwan!

317
00:32:56,883 --> 00:33:05,621
Ji-hwan! Ji-hwan!

318
00:33:08,094 --> 00:33:12,531
Ji-hwan, where did you go?
You scared us

319
00:33:16,335 --> 00:33:18,132
Hi!

320
00:33:42,628 --> 00:33:47,429
* The child I'm looking for

321
00:33:49,368 --> 00:33:55,068
* is hard to see

322
00:34:07,053 --> 00:34:13,549
Do you have a girlfriend now?

323
00:34:27,773 --> 00:34:30,243
Kyung-hee, I found Ji-hwan

324
00:34:30,243 --> 00:34:32,211
I found Ji-hwan

325
00:34:33,246 --> 00:34:37,615
Really? That's great

326
00:35:02,775 --> 00:35:04,675
Hold on

327
00:35:15,388 --> 00:35:19,119
Soo-in, let's change
our names from today

328
00:35:19,258 --> 00:35:21,761
I'm Soo-in and you're Kyung-hee

329
00:35:21,761 --> 00:35:25,331
Why?
Why do you wanna change names?

330
00:35:25,331 --> 00:35:31,668
If we do, even if we're apart

331
00:35:31,904 --> 00:35:37,604
we'll think of each other always

332
00:35:38,110 --> 00:35:42,308
That'll be fun.
You're Soo-in and I'm Kyung-hee

333
00:35:42,815 --> 00:35:46,182
When I think of it now,
it's really funny,

334
00:35:46,452 --> 00:35:51,480
but I asked people
to call me by his name

335
00:35:51,724 --> 00:35:52,918
Why?

336
00:35:54,460 --> 00:36:00,763
Well, I thought that even if
we were to split apart,

337
00:36:00,933 --> 00:36:04,334
I'd feel as if
I was always with him

338
00:36:16,282 --> 00:36:20,184
Next.
Number 42, Shim Soo-in

339
00:36:20,419 --> 00:36:22,410
- Yes
- Yes

340
00:36:27,627 --> 00:36:30,696
Kyung-hee,

341
00:36:30,696 --> 00:36:32,425
Yes

342
00:36:40,239 --> 00:36:43,800
Soo-in -- Kyung-Hee

343
00:36:44,577 --> 00:36:48,775
You're so lucky
to ride on this

344
00:36:50,049 --> 00:36:51,384
You know what?

345
00:36:51,384 --> 00:36:56,689
Nurse Park and Dr Kim
had a fling

346
00:36:56,689 --> 00:37:00,887
They were caught kissing
in the medicine room

347
00:37:01,427 --> 00:37:04,055
- Kyung-hee
- Yeah?

348
00:37:04,997 --> 00:37:07,397
I love you

349
00:37:09,135 --> 00:37:14,402
Me, too

350
00:40:48,487 --> 00:40:50,250
Ji-hwan, she's here

351
00:41:35,434 --> 00:41:37,095
Hi

352
00:41:54,286 --> 00:41:56,254
Hi

353
00:42:15,708 --> 00:42:18,199
Oh yeah, I forgot

354
00:42:18,577 --> 00:42:21,910
You had a small scar here

355
00:42:27,119 --> 00:42:31,818
So this mole
was on the left side

356
00:42:32,291 --> 00:42:34,418
I wasn't sure

357
00:43:07,292 --> 00:43:15,324
Kyung-hee's got a boyfriend

358
00:43:15,467 --> 00:43:21,030
Kyung-hee's got a boyfriend

359
00:43:21,106 --> 00:43:23,040
I'm taking her away!

360
00:43:23,142 --> 00:43:25,872
No!

361
00:43:25,944 --> 00:43:28,208
Don't take her!

362
00:43:37,923 --> 00:43:42,519
It's Ji-yoon, the one who
always borrowed romance novels

363
00:43:42,795 --> 00:43:45,161
Do you remember me?

364
00:43:49,968 --> 00:43:56,771
Hi.
I miss you

365
00:44:39,384 --> 00:44:40,753
Congratulations, be happy

366
00:44:40,753 --> 00:44:41,620
Thanks, go and eat

367
00:44:43,455 --> 00:44:46,549
See you at the reception.
Eat only two servings

368
00:44:48,794 --> 00:44:51,285
Your wish came true.
Congratulations

369
00:44:52,164 --> 00:44:54,223
Congratulations.
Thanks Ji-hwan

370
00:44:54,433 --> 00:44:55,834
Congratulations

371
00:44:55,834 --> 00:44:58,270
Thank you.
Congratulations also

372
00:44:58,270 --> 00:45:00,238
on getting back together

373
00:45:03,976 --> 00:45:07,646
How about a picture for this moment?
I'll take it for you

374
00:45:07,646 --> 00:45:11,984
Should we?

375
00:45:11,984 --> 00:45:13,781
No

376
00:45:15,387 --> 00:45:17,514
You look fine

377
00:46:06,104 --> 00:46:10,438
You have to give it to him

378
00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:23,388
Hi, Ji-hwan. It's Soo-in.
Are you doing okay?

379
00:46:24,289 --> 00:46:31,855
Of course.
Soo-in, are you doing okay, too?

380
00:46:32,331 --> 00:46:36,893
I think I'm going far away

381
00:46:38,470 --> 00:46:42,099
I really don't want to go

382
00:46:42,774 --> 00:46:47,370
What will I do if I
miss you and Kyung-hee?

383
00:46:48,814 --> 00:46:52,648
Ji-hwan,
take care of Kyung-hee

384
00:46:53,886 --> 00:46:57,222
I know without you telling me

385
00:46:57,222 --> 00:47:01,215
that you two like each other

386
00:47:01,760 --> 00:47:06,322
Here's some advice
about Kyung-hee

387
00:47:07,065 --> 00:47:09,431
Kyung-hee's favorite food are

388
00:47:09,735 --> 00:47:14,604
