and strawberry juice

389
00:47:14,907 --> 00:47:19,606
And she likes guys
who has a funny bright smile

390
00:47:20,579 --> 00:47:25,175
Look carefully
between her eyes

391
00:47:25,884 --> 00:47:29,988
If she has three wrinkles,
it means she's feeling sick

392
00:47:29,988 --> 00:47:35,016
So send her home quickly

393
00:47:37,663 --> 00:47:42,430
She likes to hold hands,
so do it often

394
00:47:43,735 --> 00:47:46,761
My beloved friend, Ji-hwan

395
00:47:48,206 --> 00:47:57,046
Today I feel like eating the
instant noodles you made for me

396
00:48:01,820 --> 00:48:03,913
Change into this

397
00:48:05,857 --> 00:48:12,164
Dad, you're really handsome,
but there's something missing

398
00:48:12,164 --> 00:48:15,930
What is?

399
00:48:16,501 --> 00:48:19,231
- Dad, come here
- Yes

400
00:48:20,138 --> 00:48:22,800
- Stay still
- Yeah

401
00:48:49,568 --> 00:48:55,598
Hi, Ji-hwan.
It's Kyung-hee

402
00:48:58,076 --> 00:49:00,840
I'm alone right now

403
00:49:01,413 --> 00:49:04,905
My dad suddenly
had to go to Seoul

404
00:49:05,350 --> 00:49:09,980
You better not laugh at this

405
00:49:11,056 --> 00:49:16,460
When I go away,

406
00:49:17,396 --> 00:49:22,493
I told him I wanted a beautiful
funeral like in the movies

407
00:49:23,101 --> 00:49:28,232
It'll probably cost a lot
since I wanted a fitted dress

408
00:49:29,875 --> 00:49:35,614
I wanted to look pretty
for people one last time

409
00:49:35,614 --> 00:49:38,708
Especially you

410
00:49:39,551 --> 00:49:42,611
I'm worried about
your company test

411
00:49:42,888 --> 00:49:47,382
Since you came to see me often,
you didn't have much time

412
00:49:48,193 --> 00:49:54,299
It was awkard and silent
between us,

413
00:49:54,299 --> 00:49:59,327
but I was happy, thinking about the old days.
How about you?

414
00:50:00,672 --> 00:50:04,768
I did, too

415
00:50:05,777 --> 00:50:10,043
I think I'm a very lucky girl

416
00:50:10,449 --> 00:50:15,443
All I have are happy memories

417
00:50:17,189 --> 00:50:22,525
Soo-in, who made me
laugh all the time

418
00:50:25,163 --> 00:50:30,294
And for making me realize how
wonderful taking pictures are,

419
00:50:31,069 --> 00:50:33,902
my beloved Ji-hwan

420
00:50:38,210 --> 00:50:44,115
Ji-hwan, a nice gentleman

421
00:50:44,382 --> 00:50:47,647
who accepted my awkward kiss

422
00:50:49,754 --> 00:50:54,885
This is embarrassing,
but I really liked it then

423
00:50:55,794 --> 00:50:59,821
I want to erase this line

424
00:51:00,031 --> 00:51:02,761
Forget it, I'm too tired

425
00:51:07,839 --> 00:51:10,569
Coming to my funeral, right?

426
00:51:11,243 --> 00:51:16,078
You have to come.
Since I miss you as well

427
00:51:16,348 --> 00:51:18,650
If a single guy
doesn't show up,

428
00:51:18,650 --> 00:51:23,246
people will feel
really sorry for me

429
00:51:24,156 --> 00:51:33,155
Oh yeah, I have something to tell you.
You might get angry at me

430
00:51:34,900 --> 00:51:39,803
Remember that letter
for Soo-in?

431
00:51:40,639 --> 00:51:44,973
I ripped it up

432
00:51:45,343 --> 00:51:51,009
I feel better now
for telling you

433
00:51:52,184 --> 00:51:55,745
You'll forgive me, right?

434
00:51:56,054 --> 00:52:01,720
I'll tell Soo-in
when I meet her

435
00:52:02,661 --> 00:52:08,224
Ji-hwan, I love you

436
00:52:10,268 --> 00:52:17,299
I loved you before
and I love you now

437
00:52:17,576 --> 00:52:23,674
Good-bye, Ji-hwan.
Good-bye
